{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-warm-up-greeting-new-colleagues/task-9","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 9","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Chen Na želi da uveri grupu ljudi. Ovo je uobičajen način da se kaže \"Zdravo, svima\" na kineskom.</p>\n<p>Zapamtite da za slab ton, treba napisati broj 5.</p>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte zvuk i dovršite sledeću rečenicu.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><ruby>你们好<rp>(</rp><rt>nǐ men hǎo</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> To je množinska forma pozdrava na kineskom. Znači \"Habari, nyote\" ili \"Habari, ninyi nyote\".</p>\n<p>Možete ga koristiti kada pozdravljate više od jedne osobe, kao kolege ili prijatelje. Na primer:</p>\n<p><ruby>你们好<rp>(</rp><rt>nǐ men hǎo</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>，<ruby>欢迎你们学习中文课程<rp>(</rp><rt>huān yíng nǐ men xué xí zhōng wén kè chéng</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>！ - Zdravo svima, dobrodošli na kurs kineskog jezika.</p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-chinese","block":"zh-a1-warm-up-greeting-new-colleagues","lang":"zh-CN","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-warm-up-greeting-new-colleagues/task-9"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>BLANK</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"你们好 (nǐ men hǎo)","feedback":"<p>Ovaj pozdrav znači \"Habari, nyote\", napisan je kao <span class=\"highlighted-text\">ni3 men5 hao3</span>.</p>"}]},"inputType":"pinyin-to-hanzi","tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-boardroom.png","characters":[{"character":"Chen Na","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_greetings_and_introductions_warm_up.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":8.98,"finishTimestamp":9.9},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Chen Na","position":null,"op